      "post_content": "Urza's block was one of the best blocks in the game. Powerhouse cards, great flavor, and some truly degenerate combos that led to some absurd shenanigans.   \n  \nThis doesn't exactly break anything, but it's a solid card advantage winner for late game, when it really counts.",
